Texts.Chs: 心线人是一个来自宇宙之外的古老种族，拥有无与伦比的技术进步水平。他们的文明在千万年前的神秘情况下崩溃了，但是一些心线人仍然存活下来，被锁在休眠舱中。
Texts.Eng: An ancient race originating from a place beyond our universe, the Centens possessed an unrivaled level of technological advancement. Their civilization collapsed under mysterious circumstances aeons ago, but some Centens still survive, locked away in stasis pods.
